{"tid":574966,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美國白宮: 不干涉中共修憲， 麥凱恩: 美國要出手","createTime":"2018-02-28T01:01:49.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-28T03:23:16.000Z","uid":134071,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"dd3cd7f756b1a596186cb47e0addf5915ab7cc6b","tid":574966,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T01:01:49.000Z","msg":"麥凱恩係少數反特朗普既共和黨人<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180227/s00005/1519699322337\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180227%2Fs00005%2F1519699322337&d=EGmk6%2FR3L2ebSb07ci6QbYM9LuuOiGKVuJxWWRW4JEQ%3D&h=74b3a6eb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180227%2Fs00005%2F1519699322337&h=c947e7e5\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180227/s00005/1519699322337</a><br />\n<br />\n【取消任期限制】白宮：中國自己決定　麥凱恩：美國須捍衛普世價值 (11:13)<br />\n<br />\n中共中央建議修憲，包括刪除國家主席「連續任職不得超過兩屆」的任期限制。美國白宮發言人桑德斯周一（26日）指出，任期限制屬於中國內政、是中國自己的決定。她又指總統特朗普在競選期間已多次指出，支持國會議員的「任期制」，但她認為中國是否廢除任期制，應由中國決定以何種方式對國家最有利。<br />\n<br />\n另外，資深參議員、共和黨重量級人物麥凱恩對中國的做法表示關注，他在個人Twitter上轉發《紐約時報》評論習近平強人統治所引發的憂慮，他指「美國必須捍衛普世價值、法治、開放的商業及尊重主權」。<br />\n（法新社/Twitter）"},{"pid":"b822ae51ba1f4531a6918a78d69b20b7f3de6f30","tid":574966,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T01:50:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee1e9300fac9a95f1eb06c697b5a4fea65e69eb4","tid":574966,"uid":171901,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T01:54:58.000Z","msg":"關麥美恩乜野事, 做你嘅主持啦！"},{"pid":"30723338198e7ec59ff46bd65bc47f8022f29c04","tid":574966,"uid":134071,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"ee1e9300fac9a95f1eb06c697b5a4fea65e69eb4","tid":574966,"uid":171901,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T